c: 43
v: 32
t: "E ko kam…ďe senndata yurmeende Joomi maa nden? Awa ko Menen woni ko senndi nguureeji ma…ď…ďe …óin hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, ka nguurndam aduna. Men …ďamti yoga ma…ď…ďe e hoore …ďeya, darjaaji, fii no yoga ma…ď…ďe jogitora yoga eeltane. Haray ko yurmeende Joomi maa nden, …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e kon ko …ďe moo…ďata"